---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | OumaShu"
  description="Learn about how OumaShu handles your data and protects your privacy. We are committed to maintaining the confidentiality and security of your information."
  keywords="privacy policy, data protection, user privacy, oumashu privacy"
>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50 dark:bg-black">
    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 hover:text-gray-900 dark:hover:text-white mb-4">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"></path>
          </svg>
          Back to Home
        </a>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-2">
          Last updated: November 16, 2024
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Content -->
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
            At OumaShu, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, 
            and protect your information when you use our website and services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Information We Collect -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
          
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">1. Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            When you visit OumaShu, we may automatically collect certain information about your device, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Operating system</li>
            <li>IP address (for language detection)</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
            <li>Referring website</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">2. Information You Provide</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We do not require you to create an account or provide personal information to use OumaShu. 
            However, if you contact us via email, we will collect your email address and any information 
            you choose to provide in your message.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">3. Local Storage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We use browser local storage to save your preferences, such as:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li>Language preference</li>
            <li>Theme preference (light/dark mode)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            This data is stored locally on your device and is never sent to our servers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- How We Use Your Information -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We use the information we collect to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
            <li>Detect language preferences for better user experience</li>
            <li>Analyze website usage and trends</li>
            <li>Respond to your inquiries and support requests</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Third-Party Tools -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Third-Party Tools and Links</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            OumaShu serves as a directory linking to third-party tools and websites. We are not responsible 
            for the privacy practices of these external sites. When you click on a tool link and leave OumaShu, 
            you are subject to the privacy policy and terms of service of that third-party website.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We recommend reading the privacy policies of any third-party sites you visit through our directory.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Cookies and Tracking -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            OumaShu uses minimal cookies and tracking technologies:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Essential cookies:</strong> Required for basic site functionality</li>
            <li><strong>Analytics:</strong> We may use analytics services to understand how visitors use our site</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            You can control cookies through your browser settings. However, disabling cookies may affect 
            your experience on OumaShu.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Data Security -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, 
            alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet 
            or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Your Rights -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Your Privacy Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            Depending on your location, you may have certain rights regarding your personal information:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            <li>Access and receive a copy of your data</li>
            <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent at any time</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            To exercise these rights, please contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@oumashu.top" class="text-sakura-600 dark:text-sakura-400 hover:underline">contact@oumashu.top</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Children's Privacy -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            OumaShu is not intended for children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect 
            personal information from children. If you believe we have collected information from a child, 
            please contact us immediately.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Changes to This Policy -->
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by 
            posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact Us -->
        <section class="bg-sakura-50 dark:bg-gray-900 rounded-lg border border-sakura-200 dark:border-gray-700 p-6">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
            If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
            Email: <a href="mailto:wanghongxiang23@gmail.com" class="text-sakura-600 dark:text-sakura-400 hover:underline">wanghongxiang23@gmail.com</a><br>
            X (Twitter): <a href="https://x.com/Rollkey4" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-sakura-600 dark:text-sakura-400 hover:underline">@Rollkey4</a><br>
            Website: <a href="https://oumashu.top" class="text-sakura-600 dark:text-sakura-400 hover:underline">https://oumashu.top</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mt-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        <p class="text-center text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
          Â© 2024 OumaShu. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</Base>

